Alpha Media Holdings (AMH) launched, NewsDay Weekender in Harare today. The colourful launch included a march from Kwame Nkrumah to the First Street kiosk and a road show, which kept the crowd entertained. Pictures by Shepherd TozvirevaAMH are the publishers of NewsDay Zimbabwe Independent, The Standard and Southern Eye.&nbsp;AMH staff marching from 1 Kwame Nkrumah Avenue to First StreetThe crowd marching from 1 Kwame Nkrumah Avenue to First Street&nbsp;NewsDay Editor Wisdom Mdzungairi giving a speech at the NewsDay Weekender launchDancers entertaining the crowd at the launchPeople reading the NewsDay WeekenderThe road show was well attended